title: Yatawatta Divisional Secretariat
text: Yatawatta Divisional Secretariat is a <a href="Divisional%20Secretariats%20of%20Sri%20Lanka">Divisional Secretariat</a> of <a href="Matale%20District">Matale District</a>, of <a href="Central%20Province%2C%20Sri%20Lanka">Central Province</a>, <a href="Sri%20Lanka">Sri Lanka</a>.
